name: B2 @ SIT Dover
directions: From The Canopy (main food court), turn right at the toilet and walk along the corridor to the next toilet. The musolla is under the staircase, beside the male toilet.
provision: Slippers, Praying Mats, Telekung, Qiblat Indicator, Quran, Fans
remarks: If the musolla is fully occupied, you can pray at the turfed open area on mezzanine level, a few steps up outside the musolla.
